":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府入面嘅暴徒聽住 ！<br />\n<br />\n如果香港市民嘅遊行活動裡面，有任何示威者被襲擊受傷甚至死亡嘅話，而你地冇全力協助防御拯救 ！<br />\n<br />\n即係話你地唔能夠代表人民去保護人民嘅生命財產 ！<br />\n<br />\n咁你地只配得被自己生產嘅卵玷污 !<br />\n<br />\n睇下你地仲有乜卵用！<br />\n<br />\n自己計下條數，你地將會承受<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10,872,000次玷污</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n註1：毅進制遊行人數<br />\n6.9 ~ 24萬人<br />\n6.16 ~ 33.8萬人<br />\n7.1 ~ 19萬人<br />\n7.21 ~ 13.8萬人<br />\n每人1打中國雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n註2： 實際玷污次數應該係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">48,120,000次或以上</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/163205_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F163205_09e95d81f988b6f6343512173f8a84d2.gif&h=284fc35a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fa33f3bc674041001d371a14d84d73efb4364dd","tid":1376141,"uid":292204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:34:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"45918aed7bc1b3fe4fc9c4edb07bd75abadfe196","tid":1376141,"uid":274539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8fac145df693a8ef9013ce71da38ae75dbf1b424","tid":1376141,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推呀 一個鐘推唔到一千個正評 叫唔到人出黎 咁係咪真兄弟呀</span>"},{"pid":"99fb3e307bf498959c8a0110fdb5c127cbbb12ed","tid":1376141,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"sogo會展都有人"},{"pid":"ad024e10604c6782533f8302ea7c8879b80ceb0d","tid":1376141,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"淨係要人咋！"},{"pid":"9ede58bb5dc8f484101523bd6807e7eab214bd01","tid":1376141,"uid":263423,"